** TKOJ TKJN
0111 IAF
** ER
E-01 UPDATE SECTION ENTRY 1 OR 2
E-02 DATE OR DIE NO. ENTRY
E-03 DATE ERROR
E-04 FACTORY CODE ERROR
E-05 NO ADDITIONAL ENTRY
E-06 NO DIE NO. IN DIE VERSION MASTER
E-07 NO REFERENCE DATA
E-08 UPDATE SECTION 0 OR 1
E-09 DIE NUMBER ENTRY
E-10 NUMBER ENTRY
E-11 MACHINE NO. ENTRY
E-12 NO MACHINE NO. IN FACILITY MANAAEMENT MASTER
E-13 CLASSIFICATION OF BREAK 1-9 OR S
E-14 SHIFT SECTION 0 OR 1
E-15 NO DATA FOR CHANGE
E-16 CMD-5 PRESS FOR CHANGE DATA
E-17 NO PREVIOUS DATA
E-18 NO FOLLOWING DATA
E-19 DIE NO. OUT OF USE
E-20 Y OR N ENTRY ONLY
E-21 SECTION ENTRY
E-22 TEAM ENTRY
E-23 SECTION AND TEAM ENTRY
E-24 MACHINE NUMBER ERROR.
E-25 MACHINE AND DIE NO.(H.N.R.T.A.W.D) CHANGE IN MASTER
E-26 MISMATCH DIE NO.WITH FACTORY CODE
E-27 DIE NO. OUT OF EXISTENCE
E-28 GREATER DATE
** ERX
 ->  DIE NO. CHECK
 ->  MACHINE NO. CHECK
 ->  '0' PRESS FOR ENTRY WITH ERROR
 ->  DIE NO. CHECK
